                        <div class="col-md-9" >

                    

                    
	

                    <!--Sharepoint's placeholder-->

                    
	
	
	
	
	
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" >The Oregon Department of Transportation (ODOT) complies with Title VI of the Civil Rights Act, the Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA), and other federal nondiscrimination authorities which prohibit discrimination based on race, color, national origin, age, disability, and sex in ODOT’s programs, activities, services, operations, delivery of benefits, and opportunities to participate in federal programs.<div><br>
ODOT's Office of Engagement and Civil Rights (OECR) has nondiscrimination policies which apply in ODOT's programs, activities, services, operations, delivery of benefits, and opportunities to participate.<br><br>
<div class="ms-rtestate-read ms-rte-wpbox"><div class="ms-rtestate-notify  ms-rtestate-read f6d8937b-70ef-477b-9b42-39c9aaf19e61" id="div_f6d8937b-70ef-477b-9b42-39c9aaf19e61" unselectable="on"><div id="MSOZoneCell_WebPartWPQ1" class="s4-wpcell-plain ms-webpartzone-cell ms-webpart-cell-vertical ms-fullWidth ">
	<div class="ms-webpart-chrome ms-webpart-chrome-vertical ms-webpart-chrome-fullWidth ">
	<div    id="WebPartWPQ1"  class="ms-WPBody "   style="" ><div id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl40_g_f6d8937b_70ef_477b_9b42_39c9aaf19e61">
		<div class="list-unstyled panel-group or-accordion-list" id="accordion-ctl00_ctl00_ctl40_g_f6d8937b_70ef_477b_9b42_39c9aaf19e61_ctl01">
			<div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-a149620c-b18c-458c-9d00-4b6d7388340e">
				<h2>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#a149620c-b18c-458c-9d00-4b6d7388340e" aria-controls="a149620c-b18c-458c-9d00-4b6d7388340e" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="3c588cb3-8fc4-4da3-bb34-e49ebc3abff0">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Nondiscrimination Programs at ODOT</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h2><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="a149620c-b18c-458c-9d00-4b6d7388340e" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass369861AB86DB487D8DFA1B6D3AADDDD6"><p></p><p>The ODOT Office of Civil Rights partners with other business areas at ODOT to serve people in Oregon in alignment with federal nondiscrimination authorities.</p><ul><li><a href="/odot/About/Pages/ADA.aspx" target="_blank">Americans with Disabilities Act</a></li><li><a href="/odot/Business/OCR/SiteAssets/Lists/Non_Dis_Main_List/EditForm/ODOT-TitleVI-Implementation-Plan.pdf" target="_blank">Title VI of the Civil Rights Act of 1964</a><br></li><li><a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Pages/Intermodal-Civil-Rights.aspx" target="_blank">Intermodal Civil Rights (Public Transportation)</a></li><li><a href="/odot/Business/OCR/SiteAssets/Lists/Non_Dis_Main_List/EditForm/ODOT-Annual-EJ-Report.pdf" target="_blank">Environmental Justice</a><br></li></ul><p>For more information, see the <strong>Related Links</strong> section further down the page.​​​​<br></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-dde71410-a957-471f-b1b6-2adea50e7671">
				<h2>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#dde71410-a957-471f-b1b6-2adea50e7671" aria-controls="dde71410-a957-471f-b1b6-2adea50e7671" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="2a4fbc33-a67c-4bca-b92e-863d1bf580d8">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">ODOT OECR assistance, concerns, and complaints</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h2><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="dde71410-a957-471f-b1b6-2adea50e7671" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass230AEDF3F39A44C19E0EDFECF6201DE1"><p>In an effort to provide equitable access, ODOT provides accessibility aids, translation, and interpretation services for all public events and vital documents free of charge upon request. You can get these services by providing reasonable advanced notice.<br></p><p>
      <strong>Contact the ODOT Office of Civil Rights directly for assistance with any of the following&#58;</strong></p><ul><li>General assistance and inquiries;<br></li><li>Translating ODOT publications;<br></li><li>Interpreting for ODOT events or activities;<br></li><li>Improving accessibility to public events;<br></li><li>Providing recourse against discrimination;<br></li><li>Locating Civil Rights program documentation.<br></li></ul><p>
      <strong>Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA) and accessibility&#58;</strong><br></p><p>If you are&#160;experiencing a barrier to access to Oregon state transportation systems or services, please let us know by completing our&#160;<a href="/odot/ADA/Pages/CQCR.aspx" target="_blank"><strong>Comments, Questions, Concerns, and Requests (CQCR)</strong></a> online form.<br></p><p>
      <strong>Title VI and Discrimination&#58;</strong><br></p><p>
   Discrimination occurs when someone treats another person unfairly or harasses that person because of what they believe about the person's protected class status. Protected classes under Title VI of the Civil Rights Act of 1964 are race, color, national origin, age, disability, and&#160;sex. Oregon recognizes additional protected classes.
   </p><p>
If you need help from ODOT related to a discrimination concern, or if you want to file a discrimination complaint with ODOT, please visit our <strong><a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Pages/Civil-Rights-Concerns.aspx" target="_blank">Civil Rights Concerns and Discrimination Complaints at ODOT</a></strong> page. This page provides information about our different concern and complaint options and links to online forms and more resources.<br>
   </p><p><strong>Contacting OECR&#58;</strong><br></p><p>To reach out to us directly, see the <strong>Contact OECR about nondiscrimination programs</strong> section below.​<br></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-a579f486-d512-417b-a588-fc4de091a33c">
				<h2>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#a579f486-d512-417b-a588-fc4de091a33c" aria-controls="a579f486-d512-417b-a588-fc4de091a33c" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="123e4aa6-f403-4cfd-9e83-ff11edec02d7">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Related Links</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h2><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="a579f486-d512-417b-a588-fc4de091a33c" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass2257BA56C6084AC48C66807BD1FE27D4"><p>
      <strong>ODOT Nondiscrimination Statement&#58;</strong></p><ul><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/ODOT-TitleVI-ADA-Notice-Eng.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT Title VI an​​d ADA notice, 
            <strong>English</strong></a></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/ODOT-TitleVI-ADA-Notice-SPA.pdf" target="_blank">Aviso de ODOT Título VI y ADA, 
            <strong>Español</strong></a></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/ODOT-TitleVI-ADA-Notice-RUS.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT Раздела VI и уведомление ADA, 
            <strong>Русский</strong></a></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/ODOT-TitleVI-ADA-Notice-VIE.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT Title VI và thông báo ADA, 
            <strong>Tiếng Việt</strong></a></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/ODOT-TitleVI-ADA-Notice-SCH.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT 第六篇和 ADA 通知，<strong>中文</strong></a></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/ODOT-TitleVI-ADA-Notice-KOR.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT 민권법 제VI조 및 ADA, <strong>한국어</strong></a>​</li></ul><p>
      <strong>Americans with Disabilities Act&#58;</strong></p><ul><li>
         <a href="/ODOT/About/Pages/ADA.aspx" target="_blank">Accessibility at ODOT Webpage</a></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/About/Pages/ADA-Transition.aspx" target="_blank">ADA Transition Plan Webpage</a><br></li></ul><p>
      <strong>Environmental Justice&#58;​</strong></p><ul><li> 
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/SiteAssets/Lists/Non_Dis_Main_List/EditForm/ODOT-Annual-EJ-Report.pdf" target="_blank">Environmental Justice Program Report​​</a><br></li></ul><p>
      <strong>Title VI of the Civil Rights Act&#58;</strong></p><ul><li>
         <a href="https&#58;//www.justice.gov/crt/fcs/TitleVI" target="_blank">Title VI of the Civil Rights Act of 1964, 42 U.S.C §§ 2000d</a><br></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/titlevi_related_authorities.pdf" target="_blank">FHWA, Selected related Title VI statutes</a><br></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/SiteAssets/Lists/Non_Dis_Main_List/EditForm/ODOT-TitleVI-Implementation-Plan.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT Title VI Implementation Plan​</a><br></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/SiteAssets/Lists/Non_Dis_Main_List/EditForm/ODOT-TitleVI-Annual-Accomplishments-Report.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT Title&#160;VI Annual Accomplishments Report</a><br></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/Documents/ODOT-Language-Access-Plan.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT Language Access&#160;Plan</a><br></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/SiteAssets/Lists/Non_Dis_Main_List/EditForm/ODOT-Title-VI-Compliance-FMCSA-Supplement.pdf" target="_blank">ODOT Title VI Compliance FMCSA Supplement</a><br></li><li>
         <a href="/odot/Business/OCR/SiteAssets/Lists/Non_Dis_Main_List/EditForm/Notice-Of-Rescission-Web.pdf" target="_blank">FHWA Title VI Notice of Rescission​</a><br></li></ul><p>
      <strong>Title VI for Certified Local Public Agencies (CLPAs)&#58;</strong></p><ul><li>
         <a href="/odot/localgov/pages/certification-guidance-forms.aspx" target="_blank">ODOT Certified Programs Office (CPO) ​Guidance and Forms​</a></li><li>Certified LPA Bulletin&#160;101-47 is available on the 
         <a href="/odot/LocalGov/Pages/certification-guidance-forms.aspx" target="_blank">ODOT CPO Title VI Annual Compl​​iance Guidance Bulletins</a>&#160;page​<br>​​​<br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-a1aec893-8d18-49d3-9711-34c681402887">
				<h2>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#a1aec893-8d18-49d3-9711-34c681402887" aria-controls="a1aec893-8d18-49d3-9711-34c681402887" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="05a6dccb-27d3-46ab-952f-c4b0a6da297c">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">Contact OECR about nondiscrimination programs</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h2><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="a1aec893-8d18-49d3-9711-34c681402887" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass36B68F88DD324000BA5A3E3E41E8ECF3">​You can email our <a href="mailto&#58;OCRINFOREQUEST@odot.state.or.us?subject=ODOT%20OCR%20information%20request" target="_blank"><strong>Administrative Office</strong></a>, our <a href="mailto&#58;ODOT_ADA@ODOT.Oregon.Gov?subject=ODOT%20ADA%20Program%20Manager%20information%20request" target="_blank"><strong>ADA Program</strong> <strong>Manager</strong></a>, or our <a href="mailto&#58;ODOT.TItleVI@ODOT.Oregon.Gov?subject=ODOT%20Title%20VI%20Officer%20information%20request" target="_blank"><strong>Title VI Officer</strong></a><strong> </strong>for assistance. You can also reach us using one of the following methods&#58;<ul><li><strong>Administrative Office Phone&#58; </strong>503-986-4350</li><li><strong>Title VI/ADA Toll Free Line&#58;</strong> 855-540-6655</li><li><strong>TTY&#58;</strong> <span data-teams="true">800-735-2900</span></li><li><strong>Oregon Relay Service&#58;</strong> 7-1-1<br></li><li><strong>Fax&#58;</strong> 503-986-6382​<br></li></ul></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div><div class="ms-clear"></div></div>
</div>
</div></div><div id="vid_f6d8937b-70ef-477b-9b42-39c9aaf19e61" unselectable="on" style="display&#58;none;"></div></div></div></div>
		</div>
	</div>

